<p><span class="anchor" id="p66"></span>أَو جهرية وَأسر فِيهَا الإِمَام<a href="#p66" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p67"></span>قَرَأَ<a href="#p67" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p68"></span>الْمَأْمُوم السُّورَة<a href="#p68" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p69"></span>فِي الْأَصَح<a href="#p69" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p70"></span>وَمُقَابِله لَا يقْرَأ مُطلقًا<a href="#p70" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p71"></span>وَيسن للصبح وَالظّهْر طوال الْمفصل وللعصر وَالْعشَاء أوساطه<a href="#p71" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>